{"tid":1829663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Solomon Yue: 如英國放生「華為」, 將反對英美貿易協議","createTime":"2020-01-19T03:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T08:11:24.000Z","uid":134071,"like":306,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"c669f59103bea7a6feebb71eed0106054ffcb2ba","tid":1829663,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"英國首相Boris Johnson將在近期內決定會否同意讓「華為」參與英國5G網絡&quot;非核心&quot;建設。<br />\n這個決定，已被廣泛視為決定Boris Johnson對中共立場的指標。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨大佬Solomon Yue表示如英國放生「華為」, 他自己將反對美國與英國簽署自由貿易協議.<br />\nSolomon Yue也強烈炮轟英領篤灰出賣香港義士.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/SNt9Bcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNt9Bcx.jpg&h=33f8dc4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/WQ3msji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQ3msji.jpg&h=ae3cbe8e&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1218691896656252929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1218691896656252929&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=3fee3807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1218691896656252929&h=3d619704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1218691896656252929</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1217416282976313346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1217416282976313346&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1PUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=4afe6f6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1217416282976313346&h=337cda79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1217416282976313346</a>"},{"pid":"b4cd6a29ceae8117dc6eb39c057092b22580bcb8","tid":1829663,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"repl